From dda9802cff43702def8684336ed08439d01f0495 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Richard Gibbs <rich_gibbs@hotmail.com>
Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 20:17:43 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 29/29] Add checktags/tagtype attributes and pragma amigaos
 tagtype.

Backport from GCC 8 adtools patches 0002, 0020, 0021. Combined into
a single patch for GCC 7:

- Rename lineartags attribute to checktags for clarity
- Add tagtype attribute for enum constants to annotate tag values
  with type information for compile-time verification
- Add pragma "amigaos tagtype" for annotating static const int tags
- Implement tag-type hash table in c-parser.c for associating enum
  values with expected pointer types
- Add tag checking in c-typeck.c convert_arguments() for functions
  marked with the checktags attribute
- Add amigaos_handle_checktags_attribute and
  amigaos_handle_tagtype_attribute handlers
---
